RequesterPunchoutVendorCard is a CardView
    left column is Requester.Employee.ResourcePicture.File
        display as portrait image
        missing image is random background
            foreground text is "<Requester.Employee.Name.Initials>"
    main column
        Requester.Employee.Name.PreferredSimpleCorrespondenceName
    right column
        text of "Email:<Requester.Employee.EmployeeWorkEmailAddress>"
        text of "Phone:<Requester.Employee.EmployeeWorkTelephone>"
